---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
---

<Layout title="Anuncie no Portal | emguapi.com">
    <Navbar />

    <main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 my-16 md:my-24 font-sans">
        <header class="text-center mb-20 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-red-base/10 text-red-base font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-base animate-pulse"></span>
                Espaço Publicitário
            </div>
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-navy-dark uppercase italic tracking-tighter leading-tight">
                Destaque sua <br/>
                <span class="text-red-base relative">
                    Marca Aqui
                    <svg class="absolute w-full h-3 -bottom-1 left-0 text-red-base/20" viewBox="0 0 100 10" preserveAspectRatio="none"><path d="M0 5 Q 50 10 100 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="8" fill="none"/></svg>
                </span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-navy-soft mt-8 text-xl leading-relaxed">
                Conecte seu negócio com milhares de moradores, turistas e leitores diários de Guapimirim e da Baixada Fluminense.
            </p>
        </header>

        <section class="mb-24">
            <h2 class="text-center text-3xl font-black text-navy-dark uppercase italic tracking-tighter mb-12">Por que o emguapi.com?</h2>
            
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-[2rem] shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-all group hover:-translate-y-2">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-red-base/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-red-base mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-navy-dark mb-3">Público Local Engajado</h3>
                    <p class="text-navy-soft leading-relaxed">Fale diretamente com quem mora, consome e vive o dia a dia da cidade. Anúncio sem desperdício de verba.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-[2rem] shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-all group hover:-translate-y-2">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-navy-dark/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-navy-dark mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"></path><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"></circle></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-navy-dark mb-3">Foco no Município</h3>
                    <p class="text-navy-soft leading-relaxed">Somos o portal focado nas demandas reais de Guapimirim. Sua marca associada a um jornalismo útil e de credibilidade.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-[2rem] shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-all group hover:-translate-y-2">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-red-base/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-red-base mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"></path><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"></polyline><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"></line><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"></line><polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"></polyline></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-navy-dark mb-3">Conteúdo Dinâmico</h3>
                    <p class="text-navy-soft leading-relaxed">Notícias diárias, guia de turismo, utilidade pública e horários de trens, garantindo acessos recorrentes.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-24">
            <div class="bg-navy-dark rounded-[3rem] p-10 md:p-16 text-white shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden">
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-red-base/20 rounded-full blur-3xl -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/3"></div>
                
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-black uppercase italic tracking-tighter mb-10 relative z-10">Como você quer aparecer?</h2>
                
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 relative z-10">
                    <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 p-6 rounded-3xl hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors">
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Banner Destaque</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-white/70 mb-4">Sua arte no topo da página inicial ou no meio das notícias de maior acesso.</p>
                        <span class="inline-block text-red-base font-black uppercase text-xs tracking-widest bg-white py-1 px-3 rounded-md">Sob consulta</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 p-6 rounded-3xl hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors">
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Publieditorial</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-white/70 mb-4">Uma matéria completa escrita sobre o seu negócio, evento ou lançamento.</p>
                        <span class="inline-block text-red-base font-black uppercase text-xs tracking-widest bg-white py-1 px-3 rounded-md">Sob consulta</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-red-base p-6 rounded-3xl relative overflow-hidden group">
                        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/20 translate-y-full group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-300"></div>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 relative z-10">Guia de Turismo</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-white/90 mb-4 relative z-10">Cadastro de pousadas, restaurantes e atrativos turísticos da região.</p>
                        <span class="inline-block text-navy-dark font-black uppercase text-xs tracking-widest bg-white py-1 px-3 rounded-md relative z-10">100% Grátis*</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-dark mb-6">Pronto para aumentar suas vendas?</h2>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
                <a 
                    href="https://wa.me/5521969400053?text=Olá!%20Tenho%20interesse%20em%20anunciar%20no%20portal%20emguapi.com" 
                    target="_blank"
                    class="w-full sm:w-auto flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-[#25D366] text-white font-black uppercase px-8 py-5 rounded-2xl hover:bg-[#20bd5a] transition-all transform hover:scale-105 shadow-xl shadow-[#25D366]/30 tracking-widest"
                >
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"></path></svg>
                    Chamar no WhatsApp
                </a>
                <a 
                    href="mailto:anuncie@emguapi.com?subject=Quero%20anunciar%20no%20emguapi.com" 
                    class="w-full sm:w-auto flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-gray-100 text-navy-dark font-bold uppercase px-8 py-5 rounded-2xl hover:bg-gray-200 transition-all tracking-widest"
                >
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"></path><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"></polyline></svg>
                    Enviar E-mail
                </a>
            </div>
            <p class="text-[11px] text-navy-soft uppercase mt-6 font-bold tracking-widest opacity-70">
                *O cadastro no Guia de Turismo é gratuito para empreendedores locais, mediante curadoria da nossa equipe.
            </p>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>